<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich XVI. von Wittelsbach, Herzog von Bayern-Landshut</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die Vermittlung des Waffenstillstands mit Jobst von Abensberg bis Lichtmess und kündigt Hans Maurer, Diener der Stadt, an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_110" id="55r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_110_r2l13"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>pfallncʒgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> bey Reyn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l14">vnd <expan>Hercʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> Jn peyern . etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_110_r2l15"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als vns eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> nehſt auf <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brıef <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l16"><expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hat / vvıe Jr mıt dem edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jobſten <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu <expan>Abemſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l17">gerett / vnd den <expan>vnwıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den er ʒu vns maint ʒu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jn gut beſtellt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l18">habt bıs auf <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen tag lıechtmeſſ ſchıerıſt künftıg . Jn derʒeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l19">ewr gnade bas verſuchen vnd mıt Jm maine ʒu reden ob Jr vns gütlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l20">geeynen mugt etc . Danken wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l21">fleıſʒ . daʒ Jr eẅch ſo <expan>gnedıklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gen vns beweıſet / Alſo ſchıken wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l22">ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> . dem wır befolhen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l23">mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dauon ʒureden . Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr fürſtenlıch gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l24">dıenſtlıch . VVas der <expan>vorg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu dıſem mal von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l25">an eẅch werbe von der <expan>obgen<ex>nanten</ex></expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . Daʒ Jr Jn darinn <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l26">verhören . gencʒlıch <expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd gütlıch von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>auſrıcht<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l27">vnd <expan>fertıg<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet . als wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> wol getrawen das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l28">wır vmb eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Erhardȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_110" id="55r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich,</ex></expan>
<expan>pfallnczgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> bey Reyn und
                                <expan>herczog<ex>en</ex></expan> in Peyern etc. </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> nehst auf
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brief <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hat, wie ir mit dem edeln
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jobsten, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                                <expan>Abemsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, gerett und den
                                <expan>unwill<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> den er zu uns maint zu
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, in gut bestellt habt bis auf <app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen tag
                                    liechtmess schierist künftig</q>02.02.1415</note>
</app>, in derzeit ewr gnade bas versuchen und mit im maine zu reden, ob ir
                        uns gütlich geeynen mugt etc., danken wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz ir ewch so
                                <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gen uns beweiset. Also schiken
                        wir zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Mawr<ex>er,</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> davon zu reden. Und
                            <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr fürstenlich gnade dienstlich, was der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewch werbe von der
                                <expan>obgen<ex>nanten</ex></expan> sache
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ir in darinn
                                <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> verhören, genczlich
                                <expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und gütlich von
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ausricht<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wellet, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> wol getrawen. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir umb ewr
                                <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Erhardi. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
